In 2039, an unknown fleet of ships has appeared out of nowhere. These ships, called Fleet of the Fog, are far more advanced then any technology that humans posses. The seas belong to them, and all trade routes by sea are now impossible. But all is not lost. Chihaya Gunzou and his crew have encountered a renegade ship of the Fog. With her help, they have a chance to even the odds against the Fleet of the Fog. 

This show is amazing. I even like the CG animation. The characters are very well developed, and the action is fantastic. Naval battles at their best. Takao best ship.

Extras included: bluray scans, clean opening and endings, drama CD, character songs, original sountrack, music videos and ship descriptions.
